<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title">Print Server</h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="para">Una autra utilizacion classica de Samba es de lo configurar per partejar las estampadoiras installadas sus un servidor Ubuntu, que siá localament o sus la ret. Amai <a class="xref" href="samba-fileserver.html.oc" title="File Server">File Server</a>, aquesta seccion permet de configurar Samba per permetre a un client quin que siá sus la ret d'utilizar las estampadoiras sens demanda de senhal.</p>
<p class="para">Per una configuracion mai securizada, vejatz <a class="xref" href="samba-fileprint-security.html.oc" title="Securing File and Print Server">Securing File and Print Server</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="links sectionlinks" role="navigation"><ul>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html.oc#samba-printserver-installation" title="Installacion">Installacion</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html.oc#samba-printserver-configuration" title="Configuracion">Configuracion</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html.oc#samba-printserver-resources" title="Ressorsas">Ressorsas</a></li>
</ul></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-installation"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Installacion</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">Abans d'installar e de configurar Samba, es preferible de dispausar d'una installacion foncionala de <span class="app application">CUPS</span>. Vejatz <a class="xref" href="cups.html.oc" title="CUPS - Print Server">CUPS - Print Server</a> per mai de detalhs.</p>
<p class="para">Per installar lo paquet <span class="app application">samba</span>, entratz la comanda seguenta dempuèi un terminal :</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo apt install samba</span>
</pre></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-configuration"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Configuracion</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">
    After installing samba edit <span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>.  Change the <span class="em emphasis">workgroup</span> 
    attribute to what is appropriate for your network, and change <span class="em emphasis">security</span> to 
    <span class="em emphasis">user</span>:
    </p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   workgroup = EXAMPLE
    ... 
   security = user
</pre></div>
<p class="para">Dins la seccion <span class="em emphasis">[printers]</span>, metètz l'opcion <span class="em emphasis">guest ok</span> a <span class="em emphasis">yes</span> :</p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   browsable = yes
   guest ok = yes
</pre></div>
<p class="para">Reaviatz Samba aprèp aver modificat <span class="file filename">smb.conf</span></p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo systemctl restart smbd.service nmbd.service</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">La configuracion per defaut de Samba partejarà automaticament tota estampadoira installada. Installatz simplament l'estampadoira localament sus vòstres clients Windows.</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-resources"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Ressorsas</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Per de configuracions mai elaboradas de Samba, consultatz los <a href="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/" class="ulink" title="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/">guidas practics Samba (en)</a></p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Aqueste guida es tanben disponible en <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0131882228" class="ulink" title="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0131882228">format papièr</a>.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><a href="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/9780596007690/" class="ulink" title="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/9780596007690/">Using Samba</a> d'O'Reilly es una autra bona font d'informacions.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Vejatz tanben lo <a href="http://www.cups.org/" class="ulink" title="http://www.cups.org/">site Web CUPS</a> per mai d'informacions sul biais de configurar CUPS.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">
          The <a href="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Samba" class="ulink" title="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Samba">Ubuntu Wiki Samba </a> page.
          </p>
        </li>
</ul></div></div></div>
